Quick Summary One-liner for each major layer

Frequency → UHF + special tags
Tags → On-metal / anti-liquid variants
Readers → 10–20 × 4-port fixed
Placement → Portals first, then ceiling
Anti-collision → Slotted ALOHA (handles hundreds fast)
Filters → First Seen → Highest RSSI → Unique DB
Logic → IN/OUT sequencing + anomaly detection
UI → Real-time dashboard with exceptions
Money → Loss prevention is usually #1 payback
